data.description: Welcome to this beautiful townhouse located at 407 Eagle Tiff Drive in the desirable Fairview Park community. This end unit townhome offers a spacious and comfortable living space, perfect for families or individuals looking for a stylish and convenient home.    As you enter the home, you will be greeted by a welcoming foyer on the terrace level, which features a bedroom and a full bath. The main level boasts a bright and airy living room with a cozy fireplace, providing the perfect spot to relax and unwind. The abundance of windows allows for plenty of natural light to fill the space, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere.    The kitchen is equipped with stainless steel appliances, offering both style and functionality. The pantry and breakfast nook overlook the private back deck, providing a lovely space to enjoy your morning coffee or entertain guests.    The primary suite is a true retreat, complete with a spa-like bathroom featuring a separate tub and shower, dual vanities, and a walk-in closet. Additionally, there is a large secondary bedroom upstairs with its own full bath.    This townhouse has been recently updated with new LVP flooring that beautifully compliments the freshly painted walls and trim. It exudes modern elegance while maintaining a neutral palette that allows for personalization.    Residents of Fairview Park enjoy access to fantastic community amenities including a clubhouse, pool, and tennis courts. With its convenient location and proximity to shopping, dining, golf and entertainment options, this townhouse offers the perfect combination of comfort and convenience.    Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this wonderful townhouse your new home. Schedule your showing today!
